window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>The complete series in a single offering!</b></p> <p><b>Sebastian's life was destroyed in mere moments.</b></p> <p>He's catapulted into a cat and mouse chase to avenge his murdered parents and regain his rightful place as Earth's ruler. By using experimental tech from his orbital palace he's guided to old allies that become more than anything he could have expected. Some of them are talented and gorgeous too, committed to helping Sebastian regain his throne.</p>"; 
